        <h2 id="post-456"><a href="http://ajaxian.com/archives/zoozio-drag-and-drop-portal-interface" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to Zoozio: drag and drop portal interface">Zoozio: drag and drop portal interface</a></h2>
        <p class="meta">Category:  <a href="http://ajaxian.com/by/topic/showcase" title="View all posts in Showcase" rel="category tag">Showcase</a></p>
        <p>We recently saw <a href="http://www.zoozio.com/">Zoozio</a>, which is a startup that isn&#8217;t out of the closet yet.</p>
<p>You will see a now-more and more familiar interface on the front page though. They have a drag and drop portal interface for us to play with :)</p>
<p><a href="http://www.zoozio.com/"><img alt="zoozio" src="http://www.ajaxian.com/archives/zoozio.png" width="767" height="285" border="0" /></a></p>
        
